Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you play me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha--? Is it a blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenhou Chuuren Poutou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He cheated!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about a deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take it by Mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The contest is 5 games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten is behind Nakanishi's single suit hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then. Round 2.\NLet's begin, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Game 2 East Round 2\NTen/Nakanishi Team has 1 Victory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Their side has the game flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But little by little I can see their strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,6,700 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Game 2\NSouth Round 1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought. It's the single suit strategy they used in the first game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a varied pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakanisi declares Riichi when he's not in Tenpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ten waits for tiles Nakanishi has already discarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't deal into his hand any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The meaning of Nakanishi declaring Tenpai is then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.51,0:01:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I follow Ten's discards I should be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:02:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This tile will pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This should pass as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,8,000 points. Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't read what those guys are aiming at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:02:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed some telling looks between Ten and Nananishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, when I dealt into Nakanishi's hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakanishi was very pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten was flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,With that. Some mistake was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Some cooperation between them was broken, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We take advantage of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:25.60,cyan,,0,0,0,,{\pos(616,84)}#/tv/shows Gentleman Gamer Society presents
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro Takeshi as Ten Takeshi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Furukawa Yuki as Igawa Hiroyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshida Eisaku as Akagi Shigeru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,BOTTOM TEXT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(664,430)}Ten: Tenho-doori no Kaidanji\N(The Blessed Way of the Nice Guy Ten)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:28.25,white-small,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,614)}Episode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,3rd Game\NEast Round 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That strange atmosphere just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling that something passed between Ten and Nakanishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakanishi's initial joy was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A flickering vision of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he do that often?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm two tiles away from a Kokusi Musou hand!\NAnd if that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have just about won!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten, I'm sorry but the power is in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. This isn't what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And not this either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,5,200 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheeeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was one Wan tile from Tenpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he throw away a double sided wait by discarding 6 and 7 sou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten was waiting for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. I see.\NBy leaving the 1 Man and West tiles in his hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't eliminae the possibility of me finishing my Kokusi Musou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He was giving me... HOPE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, I saw through your strategy, pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't win another game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,4th Game\NEast Round 4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,8,000 points from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakanishi's round as dealer is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all tied up at two games to two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a little break?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you forgotten about winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no excuse, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I take responsibility for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had in my hands such a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop that style of play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But just a little longer and I would have had a Kokusi Musou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't let that situation pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of half baked thinking is fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopeful imaginings will absolutely be taken advantage of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,People...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope allows them to get what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:08:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the majority of people that's a okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,HOWEVER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In gambling it's just the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you lose everthing because of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrust it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So. The power, hunh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And not just the wall switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the circuit breaker watched as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten's signature move is slight of hand in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Tenhou Chuuren Poutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.\NI'll have the young guys watch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Guard all the power to this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some safety in holding off his rough cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And their coordinated play is reduced to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten's pathway to victory is entirely destroyed, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,5th Game\NEast Round 1
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're disoriented because of Nakanishi's rash behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten is still an unknown quantity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,1,300/2,600 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,5th Game\NEast Round 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,8,000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,5th Game\NSouth Round 2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,2,000/4,000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're catching up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He ain't so easily understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. My brain is tired\NI need something sweet to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you go get me a Daihuku rice cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,5th Game\NSouth Round 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't count on THAT hand just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,16,00 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our current points are enough to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Last hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In the last hand, Ten is dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That means it's Ten's last chance to pull his Tenhou Chuuren Poutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't cut the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,TEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Breh, somebody snuck in next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They got in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU TRYING TO CHEAT ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Those tiles don't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a do-over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We know about your Chuuren PouTou shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow you managed to put the lights out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but by no means will we accept this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I just now cheated?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We doubt you at the very least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen and listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I've cheated or not
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't air half baked suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We, and everyone here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We fought this 5th battle with all we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,thus at this, the 11th hour
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no reason for vague accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This Mahjong game we've been playing has been true gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it not been a fair contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I've got a Chuuren PouTou or not
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,over any suspicions raised
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,if no cheating can be confirmed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the old man's Deed with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I've cheated do as you like, but on the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't cheat we've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already decided you cheated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten hasn't cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The daihuku rice cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dahuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Ten ate from the daihuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In his slight of hand, he exchanges his 14 tiles with the first tile wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he pulled that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There would be powder stuck to the tiles in the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But that powder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's none on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. We can't say it's suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten. If that's the case, can we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,TENHOU CHUUREN POUTOU
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go of this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ever do that stuff again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I PROMISE!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether by guile or cheating outright
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to win by any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he switch them with only his LEFT hand, the one without powder on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't see it at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho Doori\N(Tenho Street)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maruo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh. It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,More than that, I've got something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you be a ringer for me once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You played a mean game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fought those older than yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Each side has a pair of ringers in a total score match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the representative that comes first is the victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't end for me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while. Heh heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ishinomori, another Ringer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maruo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Komori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your consideration.\N(Kansai dialect)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,These are our ringers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's a ringer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just about time. Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,East Round 1
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is this guy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.71,0:24:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.77,0:24:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Chitoitsu.\N(all pairs hand)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're able to complete every pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,East Round 3
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.75,0:24:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitoitsu, Tanyao.\N(All pairs, tiles numbered 2-8)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.54,0:25:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A chitoitsu again?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.68,0:25:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he read my discards?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.78,0:25:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,South Round 3
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.11,0:25:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in Tenpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.14,0:26:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He ought not be able to read this surplus tile.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.02,0:26:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,unless he can peek into my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.42,0:26:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be like he's got some superpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.14,0:26:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.\NA chitoitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.91,0:26:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,THA FUUU
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.88,0:26:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.60,0:26:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet another chitoitsu?\NWaiting on a 3 Sou.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.08,0:26:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,H-how?\NIs it by mere chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.45,0:26:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.00,0:26:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I tell you the trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.94,0:26:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.94,0:26:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.34,0:26:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.34,0:26:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When the tile you want comes out your eyes follow it for an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.42,0:26:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do you think happens to the tile you're drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.97,0:26:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When you discarded the 4 Sou, you, as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.40,0:27:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,drew your next tile with your middle finger, but it slid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.91,0:27:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That is to say your eye-line shifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.80,0:27:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and the tile you draw slid to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.68,0:27:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,S-something so small!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.68,0:27:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ALL in the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.91,0:27:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Mahjong level I'm at, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.91,0:27:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite an interesting game you're having, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.77,0:27:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.91,0:27:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to mix it up with you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.17,0:27:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever folds under pressure will lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.14,0:27:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Akagi Shigeru!\NSomeone who's never been beaten.\NA peerless Mahjong player.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.17,0:28:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Ten?
